  "commit_message": "fix(server): propagate browser renderer crash to sibling CRI clients (#33943)\n\nWhen the Chrome renderer crashed, the page-level CRI client received the\nTarget.targetCrashed event and triggered spec recovery. Sibling CRI\nclients (the capture-protocol clone, cy-prompt, studio) connect over \nseparate websockets, each with their own listener for the same event,\nbut Chrome can deliver the event to those connections AFTER recovery\nhas already entered cleanup hooks like protocolManager.afterSpec().\n\nIf",
